txt.en: Destroyed many tainted barrels at Côs Braen.
Tainted barrels can be found at Côs Braen in Laerlad.\n\nYou should destroy any tainted barrels you find.
You destroyed vile Ungoledain provisions at Côs Braen, hindering the Ungoledain's plans in Laerlad. The Woodmen of Blómgard will be thankful for your efforts.
The Ungoledain feast on tainted foods that would make most ill. These barrels of tainted provisions must be destroyed.
